task.summary: Artifact list is automatically refreshed after a project or artifact build.
CloutWatch log view and logic has been replaced with AWS Log - to display log streams and events for selected function.
List of roles is loaded only when its dropdown opened - to reduce data-transfer, when there is no editing.
Added constraints to function properties and code file size. Added links to these values on aws site.
Fixed references to maven and versions of dependencies
Implemented clear text and reformat JSON for input and output. Implemented delete AWS log streams.
Fixed wrong selection of AWS Log event for selected stream.
Added dialog to show selected AWS log event item on double-click.
Function configuration details form can be collapsed or expanded.
Output can be auto-formatted on function invocation
